trans-unit.target: FastTrack Center Benefit for Azure Rights Management

trans-unit.source: You can use the FastTrack Center Benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Azure RMS in an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: You can use the FastTrack Center Benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Azure RMS in an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: The FastTrack Center Benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.
trans-unit.target: The FastTrack Center Benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.

trans-unit.source: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the FastTrack Center Benefit.
trans-unit.target: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the FastTrack Center Benefit.

trans-unit.source: To learn about the Onboarding process as well as roles and responsibilities, see <link><linkText>FastTrack Center Benefit Process for Azure Rights Management</linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.
trans-unit.target: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.

trans-unit.source: Microsoft will contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft will contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.
trans-unit.target: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.

trans-unit.source: To request assistance, sign in to the FastTrack Center (http://fasttrack.microsoft.com), go to the dashboard, select your company name, click the Offers tab, and click the request assistance button for the eligible service.
